<doc id="117723" wikidata="Q4868828" url="?curid=117723" title="Bates Township, Michigan">
<text>Bates Township is a civil township of Iron County in the U.S. state of Michigan. As of the 2000 census, the township population was 1,021, though in 2020 its population was 925.

==Geography==
According to the United States Census Bureau, the township has a total area of , of which is land and (4.49%) is water.

